BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 282 Tm (Data used: daily OHLCV bars.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 262 Tm (Calculation:) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 242 Tm (1. Use a 60-day default lookback.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 230 Tm (2. Exclude the latest bar from the baseline.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 218 Tm (3. Compute median positive historical volume.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 206 Tm (4. Compute RVOL: latest volume divided by baseline median volume.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 194 Tm (5. Compute robust z-score and robust MAD score against the historical baseline.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 182 Tm (6. Sign the pressure by the latest price return.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 170 Tm (7. Compute signed_volume_pressure = sign\(latest_return\) * max\(log\(RVOL\), 0\).) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 158 Tm (8. Rank the signed pressure cross-sectionally into abnormal_volume_score.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 138 Tm (Bands:) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 118 Tm (- Normal: below 1.5x RVOL.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 106 Tm (- Attention: at least 1.5x RVOL.) Tj ET
